{"tid":1690020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[振軍心] 今次運動嘅「手段」、「過程」、「目標」同「結果」","createTime":"2019-11-03T06:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:30:58.000Z","uid":67553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f206c2a75492544cacc77f1fc8489b089d60622a","tid":1690020,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR: 只要堅持，盡全力做黃色經濟圈，再加速蒸發香港嘅錢，我哋贏撚硬！</span><br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，運動至今持續咗就嚟五個月，大家會唔會有少少攰？少少唔知點行落去？少少灰心？如果有嘅都好正常，但係睇完呢篇文，一定要重新振作，堅持落去！只要堅持，我哋贏撚硬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「手段」<br />\n一路keep 住做所有諗到嘅抗爭方式。遊行、行仗、人鏈乜都好，keep 住要旺區冇生意做、keep 住要遊客唔嚟、最緊要係keep 住個熱度。<br />\n<br />\n「過程」<br />\n經歷恐怖份子濫捕、經濟唔好、隨時畀人炒，香港財富減少先係攬炒嘅重點<br />\n<br />\n「目標」<br />\n1）蒸發香港嘅錢<br />\n2）建立黃色經濟圈同埋巨型資本<br />\n既然武器唔夠嚟，我哋咪用更加有力嘅「錢」做武器。當我哋夠團結嘅時候，中共一定會驚。睇下點解香港依家咁少工會、冇集體談判權就知中共有幾驚我哋團結。<br />\n<br />\n「結果」<br />\n我哋唔怕被捕，因為有黃色資本會請<br />\n我哋唔怕暴政，因為可以用經濟手段反抗<br />\n<br />\n相反，<br />\n政府會怕我哋，因為我哋係社會最大stake holder<br />\n政府會怕我哋，因為我哋可以隨時唔承認佢嘅管治<br />\n<br />\n到最後，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府會好撚驚我哋，因為佢唔再係唯一管治到香港嘅政治實體</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我哋一定要堅持，盡全力做黃色經濟圈，再加速蒸發香港嘅錢，等中共殺咗我哋都冇卵取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157604f566d9f4f00fc8e0268c1ff4894e70796d","tid":1690020,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"推啦<br />\n分化公安同狗個post唔見左<br />\n行動post 11月5又無"},{"pid":"d93d4780ba469e9c5b9814fdd1e6dbc289ab00f0","tid":1690020,"uid":333204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"唔輸得啊！！"},{"pid":"901a1962d59964ec2990a3f06ed169fbed975b5a","tid":1690020,"uid":333204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"（十萬火急）有咩同遊行一樣咁重要？！？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689984</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b1b8fa40ac75b9d517f362f9bb7489cbd1ceab5","tid":1690020,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f92254c82dd9a82e7ffcfaf90ba15599dd5452","tid":1690020,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a65524d824e1dc77474e949b0752fc2f4efb0e","tid":1690020,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaba1e4ca524afb78d4b05ff5ac25499d10df33","tid":1690020,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}